  description: "Let there be magic"
  location: "Synod"
  encounter_level: 15

  read_aloud {
    text: "This is obviously a laboratory for magical experimentation. Magic circles marked with candles and glowing sigils adorn the floor. Between them are a worktable and a lectern. Two small cages stand to the side; winged snakes lie coiled inside them. At the west end of the room is a large, boiling pool, a reddish glow emanating from its depths."
  }
  read_aloud {
    condition: "First see the \\Monster{phaerimm}"
    text: "A strange conical beast floats in the air. Rows of tentacles surround a lampreylike maw at its wide base. Four arms ending in clawed digits surround this end; one arm clutches an elaborate wand. The far end of this creature terminates in a stinger."
  }
  read_aloud {
    condition: "\\Monster{Bloodfire} emerges from the pool"
